         <div type="abstract">
            <p>
               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_1996"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs
                        type="person" ref="pe__matthias_scheibeben_QGW_II_II_1957">Mathes, . . des
